684
00:51:09,443 --> 00:51:13,046
I've told you,we run two basic stories here.
我已經告訴過你了 我們刊登了兩種基本的報導

685
00:51:13,046 --> 00:51:16,709
Grunts who buy toothbrushes and deodorant for gooks:
一種是描寫陸戰隊購買牙刷和除臭劑贈予越南人民:

686
00:51:16,750 --> 00:51:18,945
"Winning of Hearts And Minds."
"獲取好感和民心"

687
00:51:19,086 --> 00:51:22,783
And combat action resulting in a kill: "Winning the War."
另一種是作戰行動的後果導致了這樣的報導: "贏得這場戰爭的勝利"

688
00:51:22,889 --> 00:51:25,414
You must have seen blood trails,
你沒有看到血腥的道路...

689
00:51:25,459 --> 00:51:26,790
drag marks?
或拖屍的痕跡?

690
00:51:26,827 --> 00:51:27,555
It was raining
當時在下雨

691
00:51:27,594 --> 00:51:28,895
sir.
長官

692
00:51:28,895 --> 00:51:31,921
That's why God passed the law of probability.
這也就是為什麼上帝要制訂或然率

693
00:51:31,965 --> 00:51:35,128
Rewrite it with a happy ending,say, one kill.
把它改寫成一個愉快的結局 也就是說 殺個人

694
00:51:35,168 --> 00:51:38,004
A sapper or an officer. Which?
工兵或軍官? 到底用哪一個?

695
00:51:38,004 --> 00:51:39,528
Whichever you say.
隨你喜歡...

696
00:51:39,573 --> 00:51:42,371
Grunts like reading about dead officers.
陸戰隊員喜歡讀一些敵方軍官死亡的報導

697
00:51:42,409 --> 00:51:43,501
Okay
好吧

698
00:51:43,543 --> 00:51:45,738
an officer. How about a general?
一名軍官怎麼樣?

699
00:51:46,971 --> 00:51:49,769
You'd like our guys to read the paper and feel bad?
你難道喜歡我們的讀者看到"星條旗報"而難過?

700
00:51:50,884 --> 00:51:54,217
In case you didn't know, this is not a popular war.
萬一你不知道 這並不是一個受歡迎的戰爭

701
00:51:54,254 --> 00:51:58,156
Our job is to report the news that the...
我們的工作就是在報導中又傳來了...

702
00:51:58,157 --> 00:52:00,289
..."why-are-we-here" civilian newsmen ignore.
"為什麼-是-我們-這裏" 等民報記者忽視的問題

703
00:52:00,327 --> 00:52:04,058
Maybe you should go out on some ops yourself.
或許你該親自上幾次前線

704
00:52:04,097 --> 00:52:06,361
You could find more blood trails
你可發現更多的"血漬"

705
00:52:06,400 --> 00:52:08,231
and drag marks.
和"拖屍的痕跡"

706
00:52:08,402 --> 00:52:10,700
I've had my ass in the grass.
我曾經身臨戰場

707
00:52:10,737 --> 00:52:12,671
Can't say I liked it much.
並不是說我喜歡這樣

708
00:52:12,773 --> 00:52:15,909
Lots of bugs and too dangerous.
因為那兒有大量的臭蟲並且很危險

709
00:52:15,909 --> 00:52:19,106
My present duties keep me where I belong:
我現在因職務纏身不能離此地 我是屬於...

710
00:52:19,146 --> 00:52:21,341
In the rear with the gear.
...後方的補給品

711
00:52:28,989 --> 00:52:30,081
Tet.
農曆新年

712
00:52:30,123 --> 00:52:31,590
The Year of the Monkey.
猴年

713
00:52:31,892 --> 00:52:34,725
Vietnamese Lunar New Year's Eve.
越南農曆新年的除夕夜

714
00:52:35,262 --> 00:52:40,359
Down in Dogpatch, the gooks are shooting off fireworks to celebrate.
越南人民會燃放煙花爆竹來慶祝

715
00:52:49,176 --> 00:52:53,010
I am fucking bored to death, man.
我都快被憋死了

716
00:52:53,280 --> 00:52:55,714
I have to get back in the shit.
我必須上前線

717
00:52:55,949 --> 00:52:59,146
I ain't heard a shot fired in anger in weeks.
我幾周都沒有聽到槍炮聲了

718
00:52:59,820 --> 00:53:04,257
Joker's so tough, he'd eat the boogersout of a dead man's nose...
小丑很大膽 他敢吃死人的鼻屎

719
00:53:05,025 --> 00:53:06,788
...then ask for seconds.
還嚷著要添食

720
00:53:07,427 --> 00:53:09,327
Listen up, pilgrim.
聽著 漫遊者

721
00:53:09,663 --> 00:53:14,362
A day without blood is like day without sunshine!
一天不見血就像是一天看不到太陽

722
00:53:14,568 --> 00:53:17,901
Joker thinks the bad bush is
小丑認為戰爭危險 還是...

723
00:53:17,938 --> 00:53:20,240
between old mama-san's legs.
女人的兩腿之間危險

724
00:53:20,240 --> 00:53:22,333
He's never been in the shit.
他從未經歷炮火連天

725
00:53:22,375 --> 00:53:23,933
Hard to talk about.
難以形容戰況

726
00:53:23,977 --> 00:53:25,178
Like on Hastings.
像我親歷海斯丁之役

727
00:53:25,178 --> 00:53:27,874
You weren't on Operation Hastings.
你沒參與該役

728
00:53:27,981 --> 00:53:29,082
You weren't even in country.
你那時甚至還沒來越南

729
00:53:29,082 --> 00:53:31,346
Eat shit and die, you fucking
去你的

730
00:53:31,384 --> 00:53:33,750
Spanish-American poge!
去吃屎吧 你這該死的反戰的西班牙裔

731
00:53:33,787 --> 00:53:37,279
I was there! I was in the shit with the grunts.
我當時就在那兒! 我確實和陸戰隊參加過那次酷戰

732
00:53:37,324 --> 00:53:40,157
Don't listen to Payback's bullshit
別聽裘白克的屁話

733
00:53:40,193 --> 00:53:41,428
Rafterman.
賴特曼

734
00:53:41,428 --> 00:53:44,727
Sometimes he thinks he's John Wayne.
他有時以為自己是約翰韋恩

735
00:53:45,332 --> 00:53:46,993
You listen to Joker.
你們聽聽小丑怎麼說

736
00:53:47,033 --> 00:53:50,264
He knows it very little.
他知道的很少

737
00:53:50,437 --> 00:53:51,870
He's never been in the shit
他從來沒有上過戰場

738
00:53:51,905 --> 00:53:53,998
'cause he ain't got the stare.
因此他缺少這種白眼瞪!

739
00:53:54,207 --> 00:53:56,869
The 1,000-yard stare.
那是一千碼的瞪視

740
00:53:57,043 --> 00:54:00,103
A Marine gets it after he's been in the shit too long.
只有久經沙場的陸戰隊員才會有這種瞪視

741
00:54:00,347 --> 00:54:04,647
It's like, it's like you've really seen beyond.
好像...好像你真的看到過似的

742
00:54:04,851 --> 00:54:08,309
I got it.All field Marines got it.
我和戰場上的陸戰隊員都有這種瞪視

743
00:54:08,355 --> 00:54:09,913
And you'll have it, too.
他也會有

744
00:54:10,023 --> 00:54:11,490
I will?
我會有嗎?

745
00:54:11,525 --> 00:54:14,961
How do you stop five blacks
你怎麼阻止五個黑人...

746
00:54:14,995 --> 00:54:16,792
from raping a white chick?
去強姦白人小妞

747
00:54:16,830 --> 00:54:18,231
Fuck you.
去你的

748
00:54:18,231 --> 00:54:20,722
Throw them a basketball.
拋一個籃球給他們

749
00:54:24,771 --> 00:54:26,500
Incoming.
是敵軍炮火

750
00:54:28,708 --> 00:54:30,733
They're outgoing!
是我軍炮火

751
00:54:32,379 --> 00:54:33,778
That ain't outgoing!
不是我軍炮火

752
00:54:33,813 --> 00:54:36,077
That ain't outgoing!Now what'd I just say?
我軍沒還擊 我剛才說什麼?

753
00:55:14,421 --> 00:55:17,481
I hope they're just fucking with us.
希望越共不打神經戰

754
00:55:17,924 --> 00:55:20,119
I ain't ready for this shit.
我還沒有做好戰鬥的心理準備

755
00:56:20,320 --> 00:56:21,844
Cease fire!
停止射擊!

756
00:56:25,925 --> 00:56:27,324
Cease fire!
停止射擊!

757
00:56:38,872 --> 00:56:40,806
The enemy...
敵軍...

758
00:56:41,007 --> 00:56:43,498
...has very deceitfully...
欺詐性地...

759
00:56:43,543 --> 00:56:46,637
...taken advantage of the ceasefire...
...利用新年停火協議...

760
00:56:46,813 --> 00:56:49,611
...to launch an offensive all over the country.
在整個越南發動攻勢

761
00:56:50,350 --> 00:56:54,343
So far, we've had it pretty easy here.
迄今為止這基地還沒有受到猛烈攻擊

762
00:56:54,387 --> 00:56:56,719
But we seem to be the exception.
這裏好像只是個例外!

763
00:56:57,157 --> 00:57:01,924
Charlie has hit every military target in Vietnam and hit them hard.
越共向越南每一軍事目標發動猛烈攻擊

764
00:57:02,162 --> 00:57:03,686
In Saigon...
在西貢市...

765
00:57:03,730 --> 00:57:08,724
...the United States Embassy has been overrun by suicide squads.
美國大使館遭越共敢死隊蹂躪

766
00:57:10,236 --> 00:57:13,672
Khe Sanh is standing by to be overrun.
溪山也有被攻陷的威脅

767
00:57:15,041 --> 00:57:18,374
We have reports that a division of N.V.A....
我們獲悉北越軍一師...

768
00:57:18,411 --> 00:57:22,507
...has occupied all of the city of Hue south of the Perfume River.
全部佔領香河南邊的順化市

769
00:57:22,882 --> 00:57:25,282
In strategic terms,
以戰略而言 北越已經將...

770
00:57:25,318 --> 00:57:26,586
Charlie's cut the country in half...
整個越南一分為二

771
00:57:26,586 --> 00:57:29,316
...the civilian press are wetting their pants...
美國民間報章大起恐慌

772
00:57:29,355 --> 00:57:31,186
...and even Cronkite is going to say
甚至連著名電視記者克隆凱特...

773
00:57:31,224 --> 00:57:33,624
the war is now unwinnable.
也聲稱越戰輸定了

774
00:57:34,594 --> 00:57:36,528
In other words...
換句話說...

775
00:57:36,663 --> 00:57:38,654
...it's a huge shit sandwich
現在的形勢猶如我們必須去...

776
00:57:38,698 --> 00:57:41,428
and we all have to take a bite.
...咬一口大便三明治

777
00:57:44,204 --> 00:57:49,164
Does this mean Ann-Margret's not coming?
那表示安瑪格莉不來了嗎?

778
00:57:53,880 --> 00:57:58,317
You go straight up to Phu Bai.
你立刻趕去富巴市

779
00:57:58,685 --> 00:58:02,246
Captain January will need you.
詹瑞上尉需要你

780
00:58:03,356 --> 00:58:07,554
And you take off that damn button.
你必須除下那該死的圓形徽章

781
00:58:07,727 --> 00:58:11,527
You can't get killed wearing a peace symbol.
你不能佩戴著和平標誌被殺

782
00:58:11,798 --> 00:58:15,256
Permission to go with Joker.
請批准我和小丑同行

783
00:58:15,568 --> 00:58:17,502
Granted.
請求已批准

784
00:58:18,071 --> 00:58:19,038
Sir
長官

785
00:58:19,038 --> 00:58:21,199
permission not to take Rafterman.
我不想賴特曼和我同去

786
00:58:21,374 --> 00:58:22,966
You still here?
你是說這兒嗎?

787
00:58:23,343 --> 00:58:27,040
Vanish ricky-tick and take Rafterman with you.
立刻帶賴特曼啟程

788
00:58:27,247 --> 00:58:29,306
You're responsible for him.
你必須負責照顧他

789
00:59:12,188 --> 00:59:15,715
Get some! Get some!
殺死這些敵軍

790
00:59:33,276 --> 00:59:34,709
baby!
寶貝

791
00:59:44,554 --> 00:59:45,221
I've got you
我已擊敗你

792
00:59:45,221 --> 00:59:46,153
mother!
渾蛋

793
00:59:51,327 --> 00:59:54,592
Anyone who runs is a VC.
誰企圖逃跑便是越共

794
00:59:54,998 --> 00:59:57,681
Anyone who stands still...
誰屹立不動...

795
00:59:57,681 --> 00:59:59,649
...is a well-disciplined VC.
...是訓練精良的越共

796
01:00:02,639 --> 01:00:06,769
You guys ought to do a story about me.
你們該寫文章報導我

797
01:00:07,243 --> 01:00:10,610
Why should we do a story about you?
我們為何報導你?

798
01:00:10,814 --> 01:00:13,476
'Cause I'm so fucking good!
因我擅長殺越共

799
01:00:13,516 --> 01:00:15,279
That ain't no shit neither.
那也不是謊言

800
01:00:15,485 --> 01:00:20,089
I've done got me 157 dead gooks killed.
我已殺死一百五十七名越南人

801
01:00:20,089 --> 01:00:22,956
And 50 water buffaloes, too.
殺了五十頭水牛

802
01:00:23,126 --> 01:00:25,321
Them are all certified.
全部已獲證實

803
01:00:25,929 --> 01:00:29,194
Any women or children?
你曾殺婦孺嗎?

804
01:00:29,332 --> 01:00:31,300
Sometimes.
有時候

805
01:00:32,068 --> 01:00:35,504
How can you kill women and children?
你怎可殺婦女兒童?

806
01:00:36,306 --> 01:00:37,773
Easy.
易如反掌

807
01:00:37,807 --> 01:00:40,640
You just don't lead them so much.
別射向目標前面

808
01:00:41,845 --> 01:00:43,540
Ain't war hell?
戰爭豈不可怕?

809
01:01:20,350 --> 01:01:22,580
We want to get in the shit.
我們自願上前線

810
01:01:22,619 --> 01:01:23,453
Down the road.
向前

811
01:01:23,453 --> 01:01:24,784
Two-five.
五團二營

812
01:01:24,821 --> 01:01:25,588
Outstanding!
好極了

813
01:01:25,588 --> 01:01:26,680
Thanks.
謝謝

814
01:01:55,251 --> 01:01:58,482
We're looking for First Platoon,Hotel two-five.
我們找五團二營第一排

815
01:01:58,521 --> 01:02:00,113
I got a bro named Cowboy.
我有好友牛仔

816
01:02:00,189 --> 01:02:01,679
You people one-one?
你們屬一團一營?

817
01:02:01,724 --> 01:02:05,558
No, sir. We're reporters for "Stars and Stripes."
我們是星條旗報記者

818
01:02:05,995 --> 01:02:08,361
I'm Cowboy's platoon commander.
我是牛仔的排長

819
01:02:08,398 --> 01:02:11,265
He's just down the road in the platoon area.
他就在前面路那一排

820
01:02:11,301 --> 01:02:12,666
May we tag along, sir?
我們可否同行?

821
01:02:12,702 --> 01:02:13,703
No problem.
沒有問題

822
01:02:13,703 --> 01:02:14,931
Welcome aboard.
歡迎加入

823
01:02:15,104 --> 01:02:18,665
I'm Schinoski. Walter J. Schinoski.
我是華特辛諾斯基

824
01:02:18,708 --> 01:02:20,869
They call me Mr. Touchdown.
他們稱我底線得分

825
01:02:21,077 --> 01:02:23,705
I played ball for Notre Dame.
我是聖母大學足球隊員

826
01:02:24,614 --> 01:02:26,707
You here to make Cowboy famous?
你來使牛仔成名?

827
01:02:26,916 --> 01:02:28,440
Never happen, sir.
永遠不會 長官

828
01:02:28,751 --> 01:02:31,117
If you came looking for a story,
如果你來找尋新聞

829
01:02:31,154 --> 01:02:32,985
this is your lucky day.
今天是你幸運日

830
01:02:33,156 --> 01:02:35,056
We got Condition Red
我們正處高度戒備...

831
01:02:35,091 --> 01:02:36,524
and we expect rain.
期望猛戰

832
01:02:36,559 --> 01:02:37,617
Outstanding.
好極了

833
01:02:37,660 --> 01:02:39,093
We taking care of business?
我軍已有對策?

834
01:02:39,495 --> 01:02:42,365
The N.V.A. are dug in deep.
北越軍備妥固守

835
01:02:42,365 --> 01:02:46,062
Hotel Company is working this side of the river, house by house.
我軍在河這邊逐屋搜索敵人

836
01:02:46,202 --> 01:02:48,363
Charles has his shit together,
北越軍頑強防守

837
01:02:48,404 --> 01:02:50,770
but we're still getting some decent kills.
但我軍仍有收穫

838
01:02:50,807 --> 01:02:54,877
We heard the N.V.A. executed a lot of gook civilians.
聽說北越軍處死大量平民

839
01:02:54,877 --> 01:02:56,674
Affirmative.
確有其事

840
01:02:56,846 --> 01:03:00,646
I saw bodies half a klick this side of the canal.
我在運河這邊半公里見有屍體

841
01:03:00,683 --> 01:03:02,412
Can you show me where?
你能指示所在嗎?

842
01:03:29,812 --> 01:03:32,576
The dead have been covered with lime.
屍體已被石灰掩蓋

843
01:03:33,983 --> 01:03:36,577
The dead know only one thing:
死者只知一事

844
01:03:37,553 --> 01:03:39,714
It is better to be alive.
活著比較好些

845
01:03:50,566 --> 01:03:51,999
I make it 20.
我點數二十具

846
01:03:52,035 --> 01:03:53,969
Is that the official body count, sir?
這是官方數字?

847
01:03:54,337 --> 01:03:55,702
What outfit are you with?
你屬那部隊?

848
01:03:55,838 --> 01:03:57,829
We're from "Stars and Stripes."
星條旗軍報記者

849
01:03:59,208 --> 01:04:00,043
I'm Sergeant Joker
我是小丑中士

850
01:04:00,043 --> 01:04:01,977
and this photographer is Rafterman.
攝影師賴特曼

851
01:04:02,512 --> 01:04:04,070
I'm Lt. Cleves. Hartford.
我是克萊夫少尉

852
01:04:04,113 --> 01:04:05,314
Connecticut
康乃迪克人

853
01:04:05,314 --> 01:04:06,804
Have you got a body count, sir?
你有整體數目嗎?

854
01:04:06,949 --> 01:04:08,439
Twenty.
二十具屍首

855
01:04:08,484 --> 01:04:10,111
How did it happen, sir?
慘劇如何發生?

856
01:04:10,853 --> 01:04:14,550
The N.V.A. came in with a list of gook names:
越共帶來一紙越南人名單

857
01:04:14,824 --> 01:04:17,193
Government officials, policemen,
包括政府官員 警察

858
01:04:17,193 --> 01:04:19,218
ARVN officers, teachers.
南越軍官和教師等

859
01:04:19,595 --> 01:04:22,086
They asked them, real polite
越共禮貌地請他們次日來

860
01:04:22,131 --> 01:04:24,759
to report the next day for political re-education.
受政治再教育

861
01:04:25,535 --> 01:04:27,901
Everybody who turned up got shot.
凡報到者皆被槍殺

862
01:04:28,037 --> 01:04:29,937
Some they buried alive.
有些人更遭活埋

863
01:04:35,578 --> 01:04:38,342
What is that button on your body armor?
你防彈衣上什麼徽章?

864
01:04:38,581 --> 01:04:39,980
A peace symbol, sir.
和平象徵 長官

865
01:04:40,083 --> 01:04:41,277
Where did you get it?
那裏得來的?

866
01:04:41,384 --> 01:04:43,011
I don't remember, sir.
我記不起

867
01:04:43,052 --> 01:04:45,043
What is written on your helmet?
你頭盔寫有什麼?

868
01:04:45,088 --> 01:04:46,783
"Born to Kill," sir.
"天生殺人"

869
01:04:46,823 --> 01:04:48,391
You put "Born to Kill" on your helmet
頭盔寫"天生殺人"...

870
01:04:48,391 --> 01:04:49,915
and wear a peace button.
戴和平章

871
01:04:49,959 --> 01:04:52,257
Is that some kind of sick joke?
是否病態的開玩笑?

872
01:04:52,962 --> 01:04:54,793
Well, what does it mean?
什麼意思?

873
01:04:55,098 --> 01:04:56,224
I don't know, sir.
我不知道 長官

874
01:04:56,265 --> 01:04:57,493
You don't know very much.
你不知道的很多

875
01:04:58,301 --> 01:05:02,203
Get your head and your ass wired together or I will shit on you!
你頭腦要清醒些否則有麻煩

876
01:05:02,472 --> 01:05:06,067
Answer my question or you'll stand tall before the Man.
答覆我問題否則遭紀律處分

877
01:05:06,209 --> 01:05:08,643
I was referring to the duality of man
我意指人類二重性

878
01:05:08,678 --> 01:05:09,378
sir.
長官

879
01:05:09,378 --> 01:05:11,346
The duality of man.
人類二重性

880
01:05:11,414 --> 01:05:12,938
The Jungian thing, sir.
卡爾容理論

881
01:05:14,150 --> 01:05:15,418
Whose side are you on?
你支持美國或北越?

882
01:05:15,418 --> 01:05:16,407
Our side, sir.
我們美國

883
01:05:16,486 --> 01:05:17,420
Don't you love your country?
你不愛自己國家?

884
01:05:17,420 --> 01:05:18,387
Yes, sir.
我愛國

885
01:05:18,421 --> 01:05:23,222
Then get with the program. Jump on the team and come in for the big win.
那麼支持美國努力作戰取勝

886
01:05:23,459 --> 01:05:26,758
I ask that my Marines obey my orders
我要求陸戰隊像聽從上帝般...

887
01:05:26,796 --> 01:05:28,491
as they would the word of God.
服從我命令

888
01:05:28,631 --> 01:05:30,963
We are helping the Vietnamese,because inside every gook...
我們正幫助越南人 因每一...

889
01:05:31,000 --> 01:05:34,670
...is an American trying to get out.
越南人心中都願做美國人

890
01:05:34,670 --> 01:05:36,160
It's a hardball world, son.
這是個危險世界 孩子

891
01:05:36,372 --> 01:05:37,930
We must keep our heads
我們須保持冷靜直到...

892
01:05:37,974 --> 01:05:39,441
until this peace craze blows over.
瘋狂和平運動消散

893
01:05:51,754 --> 01:05:55,554
We're looking for First Platoon,Hotel two-five.
我們找尋第五團二營一排

894
01:05:55,591 --> 01:05:56,990
Around the back.
就在後面

895
01:06:06,002 --> 01:06:07,230
First Platoon?
第一排在哪裏?

896
01:06:07,270 --> 01:06:08,464
Through there.
從那裏通過

897
01:06:32,828 --> 01:06:34,090
Hey, Lone Ranger.
喂! 獨行俠

898
01:06:38,901 --> 01:06:42,234
Holy shit!
令人驚喜

899
01:06:47,677 --> 01:06:51,272
I hoped I'd never see you again,
希望永不再見到你

900
01:06:51,314 --> 01:06:52,781
you piece of shit!
你這渾蛋

901
01:06:53,216 --> 01:06:54,979
What's happening?
近況怎樣?

902
01:06:55,184 --> 01:06:58,454
Just waiting to get back to the land of the big PX.
正等待回美國去

903
01:06:58,454 --> 01:07:02,584
Here or there, samey-same.Why go back?
為何回國? 這裏那裏都一樣

904
01:07:02,625 --> 01:07:03,523
Been getting any?
可有尋歡?

905
01:07:03,559 --> 01:07:04,150
Only your sister.
只和你妹

906
01:07:04,193 --> 01:07:05,888
Better my sister than my mom
和我妹好過我媽

907
01:07:05,928 --> 01:07:07,361
though my mom's not bad.
但我媽不錯

908
01:07:08,798 --> 01:07:09,699
Hey, you hogs
你們色情豬玀

909
01:07:09,699 --> 01:07:10,723
listen up!
聽著

910
01:07:11,567 --> 01:07:13,336
This is my bro, Joker
這是我好友小丑

911
01:07:13,336 --> 01:07:14,325
from the island
巴里島同僚

912
01:07:14,370 --> 01:07:15,098
And this is....
這位是...

913
01:07:15,137 --> 01:07:18,664
They're from "Stars and Stripes."
他們是星條旗報記者

914
01:07:18,708 --> 01:07:20,232
You'll be famous.
你們將會成名

915
01:07:21,544 --> 01:07:23,671
We're the Lusthog squad.
我們色情豬班

916
01:07:23,713 --> 01:07:26,045
We're lifetakers and heartbreakers.
我們殺人也傷人心

917
01:07:26,382 --> 01:07:29,647
We shoot holes in them and fill them with lead.
我們專射殺越共

918
01:07:34,323 --> 01:07:36,848
Are you a photographer?
你是攝影記者嗎?

919
01:07:38,527 --> 01:07:41,428
I'm a combat correspondent.
不 我是戰地記者

920
01:07:42,031 --> 01:07:44,727
You seen much combat?
你見過很多戰役嗎?

921
01:07:47,169 --> 01:07:49,899
I've seen a little on TV.
我在電視看到一些

922
01:07:53,909 --> 01:07:57,140
You're a real comedian.
你真是個滑稽客

923
01:07:57,980 --> 01:08:00,540
Well, they call me the Joker.
他們稱我小丑

924
01:08:01,984 --> 01:08:04,612
Well, I've got a joke for you.
我有個笑話給你

925
01:08:04,687 --> 01:08:09,454
I'm going to tear you a new asshole.
我要扯裂你肛門給你新的

926
01:08:11,093 --> 01:08:13,186
Well, pilgrim...
漫遊者

927
01:08:13,229 --> 01:08:18,223
...only after you eat the peanuts out of my shit!
除非你能在我大便中吃花生

928
01:08:23,873 --> 01:08:26,535
You talk the talk.
你口氣強硬

929
01:08:26,942 --> 01:08:29,433
Do you walk the walk?
或你只動口不動手?

930
01:08:34,250 --> 01:08:36,115
You might not believe it...
你或許不會相信...

931
01:08:36,152 --> 01:08:41,215
...but under fire, Animal Mother is a truly fine human being.
野獸大致上是優秀的戰士

932
01:08:41,424 --> 01:08:45,554
He just needs grenades thrown at him the rest of his life.
他一生只需有人向他投手榴彈

933
01:08:53,602 --> 01:08:54,796
Jungle bunny.
黑鬼

934
01:08:55,037 --> 01:08:57,631
Thank God for the sickle cell, huh?
多謝上帝患鏈形血球癥

935
01:08:57,940 --> 01:08:58,872
Yeah, Mother.
對了 畜生

936
01:09:00,876 --> 01:09:02,605
Hey, photographer!
喂! 攝影師

937
01:09:04,246 --> 01:09:06,111
Want to take a good picture?
拍攝精彩照片嗎?

938
01:09:07,550 --> 01:09:10,383
Take this.
拍攝他

939
01:09:19,662 --> 01:09:22,290
This...is my bro.
這是我好友

940
01:09:32,108 --> 01:09:33,905
This is his party.
這是他的宴會

941
01:09:34,377 --> 01:09:36,208
He's the guest of honor.
他是宴會貴賓

942
01:09:37,446 --> 01:09:40,540
Today is his birthday.
今天是他生日

943
01:09:40,950 --> 01:09:43,180
Happy birthday, zipperhead!
生日快樂 笨蛋

944
01:09:44,520 --> 01:09:46,750
I will never forget this day.
我永不忘今日

945
01:09:47,089 --> 01:09:52,527
The day I came to Hue city and fought one million N.V.A. gooks.
今天我來順化和百萬越共作戰

946
01:09:52,928 --> 01:09:55,761
I really love the little Commie bastards.
我確愛那共黨小雜種

947
01:09:56,766 --> 01:09:58,233
These enemy grunts are as hard
這些敵軍像斜眼的...

948
01:09:58,267 --> 01:09:59,962
as slant-eyed drill instructors.
教育班長那般強悍

949
01:10:01,904 --> 01:10:04,566
These are great days we're living!
我們生活在偉大時代中

950
01:10:06,008 --> 01:10:07,676
We are jolly green giants,
我們是強大巨人

951
01:10:07,676 --> 01:10:09,507
walking the earth with guns.
全身武裝漫步地球

952
01:10:10,846 --> 01:10:13,474
These people we wasted here today...
我們今天殺死的這些人

953
01:10:13,582 --> 01:10:16,107
...are the finest people we will ever know.
將是我們所知最優秀的人類

954
01:10:18,521 --> 01:10:20,421
Once we rotate back to the world,
我們一旦返美國後

955
01:10:20,456 --> 01:10:22,981
we'll miss not having anyone worth shooting.
將無人值得我們射擊

956
01:11:59,522 --> 01:12:02,491
Delta 6 Actual, this is Murphy. Over.
三角洲六 這是墨菲 通話

957
01:12:10,900 --> 01:12:14,802
We are receiving incoming fire from the ville.
我們遭村落炮火轟擊

958
01:12:14,904 --> 01:12:16,633
The lieutenant is down.
少尉已死

959
01:12:16,672 --> 01:12:18,503
We'll stop and check out what's in front of us.
我們暫停 偵查前面情況

960
01:12:25,014 --> 01:12:27,574
Okay, Lusthog squad, listen up!
好吧 色情豬班 聽著

961
01:12:28,250 --> 01:12:30,810
We'll move up these two roads.
我們沿此兩條路前進

962
01:12:30,886 --> 01:12:33,088
I want the third team up this road.
第三隊在這路上

963
01:12:33,088 --> 01:12:36,489
First and second team behind me up this other road.
其他一路第一第二隊跟隨我後

964
01:12:37,459 --> 01:12:39,825
Let's go! Let's get it done!
我們開始行動 走吧

965
01:17:07,429 --> 01:17:10,523
Is that you, John Wayne? Is this me?
是你嗎? 約翰韋恩? 這是我

966
01:17:10,566 --> 01:17:13,899
Start the cameras.This is "Vietnam: The Movie"!
搖動攝影機 是越南 電影

967
01:17:13,936 --> 01:17:16,405
If Joker is John Wayne, I'm a horse!
小丑若是約翰韋恩 我就是馬

968
01:17:16,405 --> 01:17:18,066
T.H.E. Rock can be a rock!
"貓竊賊"電視劇可能是岩石

969
01:17:18,106 --> 01:17:19,095
I'll be Ann-Margret!
我將是安瑪格莉

970
01:17:19,141 --> 01:17:21,176
Animal Mother can be a rabid buffalo!
畜生渾蛋可能患水牛病

971
01:17:21,176 --> 01:17:22,643
I'll be General Custer!
我將是卡斯楚將軍

972
01:17:22,678 --> 01:17:23,804
Who'll be the Indian?
誰是印地安人?

973
01:17:23,846 --> 01:17:26,576
We'll let the gooks play the Indians!
我們讓越南人演印地安人

974
01:18:05,120 --> 01:18:06,849
You're going home now.
你們現在回家去了

975
01:18:10,759 --> 01:18:12,283
Semper fi.
永遠忠誠

976
01:18:15,731 --> 01:18:17,926
We're mean Marines, sir.
我們是兇殘陸戰隊 長官

977
01:18:21,737 --> 01:18:23,671
Go easy, bros.
安心去吧

978
01:18:27,976 --> 01:18:30,035
Better you than me.
你們喪生好過我死

979
01:18:33,815 --> 01:18:36,306
At least they died for a good cause.
至少他們有好理由捐軀

980
01:18:37,386 --> 01:18:39,354
What cause was that?
什麼理由?

981
01:18:41,089 --> 01:18:42,852
Freedom.
自由

982
01:18:43,458 --> 01:18:45,926
Flush out your head gear, New Guy.
頭腦清醒些 菜鳥

983
01:18:48,063 --> 01:18:50,725
You think we waste gooks for freedom?
你想我們為自由而殺越南人

984
01:18:52,100 --> 01:18:54,591
This is a slaughter.
這越戰簡直是屠殺

985
01:18:55,370 --> 01:18:59,807
If I get my balls blown off for a word...
如我因一字連睪丸都被炸去

986
01:19:00,108 --> 01:19:03,509
...my word is "poontang."
這字就是陰道

987
01:19:05,747 --> 01:19:08,648
Tough break for Hand Job.
自慰真不幸

988
01:19:09,451 --> 01:19:13,046
He was set to get shipped out on a medical.
他本可因醫療退役送回國

989
01:19:14,389 --> 01:19:16,448
What was wrong with him?
他健康有何不妥?

990
01:19:18,660 --> 01:19:21,959
He was jerking off ten times a day.
他每天自慰十次

991
01:19:23,131 --> 01:19:27,329
It's no shit. At least ten times a day.
真的 他至少每天十次

992
01:19:28,503 --> 01:19:34,237
Last week he was sent to Da Nang to see the Navy head shrinker.
上周他奉命去峴港受精神治療

993
01:19:34,376 --> 01:19:38,574
The crazy fucker jerks off in the waiting room.
那瘋狂呆子竟在候診室自慰

994
01:19:38,847 --> 01:19:42,715
Instant Section 8.
因精神問題須立刻退役

995
01:19:42,751 --> 01:19:45,184
He was waiting for his papers to clear division.
他正等待上級師部批准

996
01:19:48,084 --> 01:19:49,381
Ready?
準備好嗎?

997
01:19:49,485 --> 01:19:50,645
Turnover.
準備拍攝

998
01:19:52,388 --> 01:19:54,879
Hue city interviews. Roll 34.
訪問順化市 第三十四景

999
01:19:56,859 --> 01:20:02,991
This is a major city,so we have to assault with...
這是大城市 因此我軍須動用

1000
01:20:03,032 --> 01:20:07,366
They send us in first squad...tanks in the streets.
坦克在街道進攻 我們第一隊

1001
01:20:07,403 --> 01:20:14,241
...to make sure there are no little, uh...Vietnamese waiting with B-40 rockets
攻入市區確保沒有北越火箭炮

1002
01:20:14,310 --> 01:20:15,678
to blow the tanks away.
轟毀我軍坦克

1003
01:20:15,678 --> 01:20:18,306
So we roll the tanks in and basically,
我軍坦克進城

1004
01:20:18,347 --> 01:20:20,781
blow the place to hell.
基本上毀滅全市

1005
01:20:21,083 --> 01:20:24,917
When we're in Hue, in Hue city...
我們進入順化市

1006
01:20:25,021 --> 01:20:29,185
...it's like a war, you know.
整個城市好像戰場一般

1007
01:20:29,225 --> 01:20:35,186
Like what I thought about, what l thought a war was supposed to be.
就像我想像中的戰爭那樣

1008
01:20:36,065 --> 01:20:38,260
There's the enemy, kill them.
如發現敵軍 殺死他們

1009
01:20:38,768 --> 01:20:42,829
There's no question about it. We're the best.
毫無疑問陸戰隊最佳

1010
01:20:42,872 --> 01:20:44,703
It's bullshit about Air Cav.
陸軍空中騎兵師徒具虛名

1011
01:20:44,740 --> 01:20:46,731
When the shit hits the fan, who do they call?
戰局危急他們...

1012
01:20:46,776 --> 01:20:49,768
They call Mother Green
只得向陸戰隊求助

1013
01:20:50,346 --> 01:20:53,281
Do I think America belongs in Vietnam?
我認為美軍該在越南作戰?

1014
01:20:53,883 --> 01:20:57,512
I don't know. I belong in Vietnam,I'll tell you that.
我不知 只知我該在越南作戰

1015
01:20:58,120 --> 01:21:00,782
Can I quote L.B.J.?
我可否引述詹森總統嗎?

1016
01:21:01,724 --> 01:21:04,060
I will not send...
我不願派遣...

1017
01:21:04,060 --> 01:21:07,996
...American boys 10,000 miles around the world...
美國男孩遠赴一萬哩外...

1018
01:21:08,030 --> 01:21:10,599
...to do a job Asian boys
去做該由亞洲男孩自己...

1019
01:21:10,599 --> 01:21:12,191
should be doing for themselves
去做的工作

1020
01:21:13,936 --> 01:21:16,234
Personally, I think...
我個人認為

1021
01:21:16,305 --> 01:21:19,638
...they don't want to be involved in this war.
越南人不願捲入戰爭中

1022
01:21:19,775 --> 01:21:24,439
I think they sort of... took away our freedom and gave it
他們取走我們的自由

1023
01:21:24,480 --> 01:21:27,813
to the gooks. They don't want it.
贈與越南人 他們卻不要自由

1024
01:21:28,184 --> 01:21:30,686
They'd rather be alive than free.
他們認為活命好過自由

1025
01:21:30,686 --> 01:21:32,654
Poor dumb bastards.
可憐愚蠢雜種

1026
01:21:33,556 --> 01:21:37,253
The ones I'm fighting at are some pretty...
我的對手越共軍

1027
01:21:37,293 --> 01:21:38,783
...pretty bad boys. I'm not real, uh....
相當驍勇善戰

1028
01:21:38,828 --> 01:21:43,925
I'm not real keen on...
我對同一戰線的...

1029
01:21:43,999 --> 01:21:48,337
...these fellows that are supposedly on our side.
許多南越軍很不滿意

1030
01:21:48,337 --> 01:21:50,931
I keep meeting them coming the other way.
我發現他們臨陣退縮

1031
01:21:54,610 --> 01:21:57,079
We get killed for these people
我們為越南人民戰死

1032
01:21:57,079 --> 01:21:59,138
and they don't even appreciate it.
但他們毫無感激

1033
01:21:59,715 --> 01:22:01,580
They think it's a big joke.
他們認為天大笑話

1034
01:22:02,318 --> 01:22:04,843
If you ask me...
如你問我的話

1035
01:22:04,887 --> 01:22:07,185
...we're shooting the wrong gooks.
我們選錯敵軍作戰

1036
01:22:07,223 --> 01:22:08,724
It depends. I'm here
須看情況

1037
01:22:08,724 --> 01:22:11,124
to take combat photos.
我工作屬拍攝戰場照片

1038
01:22:11,193 --> 01:22:14,424
But if the shit gets too thick,I'll go to the rifle.
如戰況危急我會持槍作戰

1039
01:22:15,531 --> 01:22:18,500
What do I think of America's involvement in the war?
我對美國牽涉越戰看法?

1040
01:22:18,601 --> 01:22:20,626
I think we should win.
